---
// GrowthTrap.astro - Problem framework section
---

<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white section-divider">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        The "Growth Trap" Most B2B Teams Face
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        You're caught between two challenging paths - and both make it hard to prove ROI quickly enough.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two Column Problem Framework -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Left Column - Building In-House Team -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Building an In-House Team
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">6+ months to hire, onboard, and get productive</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Â£150k+ in salaries before you see results</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Need multiple specialists: paid media, SEO, analytics, CRO</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
