          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Closer -->
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-800">
        <strong class="text-primary-600">The Result:</strong> You're under pressure to demonstrate progress, but you lack the strategic capacity to execute efficiently. You need a more agile approach.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>